description: Lists versions of an evaluation form in the specified Amazon Connect instance.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Connect instance. You can find the instance ID in the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the instance.

parameters.name: EvaluationFormId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the evaluation form.

nested_items.name: EvaluationFormVersionSummaryList
nested_items.description: Provides details about a list of evaluation forms belonging to an instance.

nested_items.name: EvaluationFormArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the evaluation form resource.

nested_items.name: EvaluationFormId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the evaluation form.

nested_items.name: EvaluationFormVersion
nested_items.description: A version of the evaluation form.

nested_items.name: Locked
nested_items.description: The flag indicating whether the evaluation form is locked for changes.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the evaluation form.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the evaluation form was created.

nested_items.name: CreatedBy
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the user who created the evaluation form.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the evaluation form was last updated.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedBy
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the user who last updated the evaluation form.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, this is the token for the next set of results.
